id: BT28
name: Birthday Tournament 28
text: |
  Unless explicitly permitted by the Diplonomic 2020 rules, all
  Contestants SHALL NOT engage in any behaviors outside of
  Diplonomic 2020 as part of negotiations or other activities
  intended to influence the course of Diplonomic 2020. Unless
  explicitly permitted by the Diplonomic 2020 rules, all Contestants
  SHALL NOT make use of loopholes in the underlying game of
  Diplomacy in order to gain a competitive advantage.

  Unless explicitly prohibited by the Diplonomic 2020 rules,
  Contestants are encouraged to lie and cheat each other and SHOULD
  NOT be found in violation of "No Faking" for actions taken within
  Diplonomic 2020.  
history:
- change:
    type: enactment
  date: 2020-07-09
  agent:
    tournament_change:
      name: 2020 Birthday Tournament
      person: Publius Scribonious Scholasticus
